## Unchanged in v2.2

All v2.1 features and fixes are intact. This release is a single targeted bug fix.

- Error Catalog tab — deduplicated error table, live search, CSV export
- Error Library search in Settings
- IL publisher attribution fix
- Ctrl+Enter / Cmd+Enter shortcut
- Nav order: Validate · Schema Reference · History / Export · Error Catalog · Info
- TX OCA validation (schema v3.0.0)
- IL AOIC validation (schema v3.1.0, 37 entity types)

